<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>dotnet-core on Wayne's blog | 偉恩的部落格 | 技術博客</title><link>https://wayneblog.ga/tags/dotnet-core/</link><description>Recent content in dotnet-core on Wayne's blog | 偉恩的部落格 | 技術博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-tw</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 11 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://wayneblog.ga/tags/dotnet-core/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>.NET SqlClient 安全漏洞 CVE-2022-41064 解讀</title><link>https://wayneblog.ga/2022-11-11/dotnet-cve-2022-41064/</link><pubDate>Fri, 11 Nov 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://wayneblog.ga/2022-11-11/dotnet-cve-2022-41064/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/52491745274_95b2fa11ec_o.jpg" alt="Featured image of post .NET SqlClient 安全漏洞 CVE-2022-41064 解讀" />&lt;style>
